## Handheld/tablet strain (Steam-Deck-class x86_64 devices): same package
## set as workstation -- real differentiation is runtime/session config
## (on-screen keyboard, UI text scaling, Big Picture autostart), not a
## package-list difference, so it lives in handheld/setup-handheld-ui.sh
## instead of here. Run that script post-install/first-login.
ubuntu-desktop-minimal
flatpak
gnome-shell-extensions
gnome-tweaks
gamemode
mangohud
winetricks
